headline: Republicans may need an AI boom to have any hope of paying for their 'one big, beautiful bill'
summary: President Trump is promising blockbuster economic growth in part because it is needed to pay for his 'big, beautiful bill.' Even wary economists say there is one long-shot way it could happen: an AI-fueled boom.
